<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="performance-n">performance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'fɔːməns/    美 /pər'fɔːrməns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>表演；演出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>give a live performance</strong>
现场表演</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>put on <strong>a performance of</strong> Hamlet 
上演《哈姆雷特》</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 表现；业绩：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>academic performance
学业成绩</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His performance at school has greatly improved. 
他在学校的表现进步很大。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My <strong>good performance</strong> in the job interview left me optimistic about my future.
在求职面试中的良好表现让我对未来感到很乐观。</p><footer>2014 安徽</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He criticized the recent <strong>poor performance of</strong> the company. 
他批评公司近期业绩不佳。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Your <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (perform) as a student will be excellent if you develop a habit of reflecting on how you learn.  （2012 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. performance  </p></div>